    "prompt": "Create a 3:4 vertical Xiaohongshu cover image for a friendly product-recommendation post. Keep the reference images’ core product forms, packaging style, illustrations, colors, typography vibe, and all existing brand elements of “Holly Shit开心拉屎”; do not invent new logos, certifications, price tags, or fake app UI. The cover should feel like a witty friend sharing cute desk items that make slacking off at work more fun, turning the products into a small life solution for stressful office moments. Main visual: one to three brand products as the first focal point, occupying about 65%-70% of the frame, arranged in a playful office desk / cubicle corner scene with casual props like keyboard edge, sticky notes, mug, papers, and soft clutter, suggesting “摸鱼” in a relatable everyday way. Composition should leave safe margins around the products and top-left or upper area for text, without covering key product details. Use bright, cheeky, slightly absurd but clean styling: high-saturation accent colors from the brand materials, with a light neutral desk base, warm daylight mixed with soft indoor ambient light, crisp product texture, editorial still-life photography with graphic-design sensibility, trendy Xiaohongshu cover aesthetic, humorous yet tasteful, not commercial-heavy. Add a small secondary text line in Chinese, lighter weight, such as “办公室摸鱼小道具” or “看到会笑的桌面文创”, placed as a smaller support info block. Only two text layers total. The main Chinese title must appear exactly as: “3个让人笑出来的摸鱼文创” in large bold Chinese typography, highly legible, friendly and lively, integrated as the cover headline. The mood should feel relieving, anti-anxiety, rebellious but cute, with a subtle joke energy rather than aggressive vulgarity. Ensure the cover clearly communicates click reason first, then lets later images explain details.",
